Heskel is the woman who watches the tree farming patch in Falador Park. She is a member of the Group of Advanced Gardeners.

Players can speak to Heskel as one of the 5 gardeners in the Fairytale I - Growing Pains quest.

Shop[edit | edit source]

Heskel also sells basic farming tools, which can be accessed by talking to her and asking Can you sell me something? It is not an actual shop and it has no set stock; each item has to be bought individually through the dialogue.
